OL,6,FWessex Water will pay #11 million
OL,7,Ftoward upgrades after the regulator
OL,8,Ffound it failed to properly manage its
OL,9,Fwastewater network.
OL,11,FThe water company, which serves
OL,12,Fregions including Dorset, Somerset and
OL,13,FWiltshire, has been made to pay the
OL,14,Fenforcement package by industry
OL,15,Fregulator Ofwat.
