OL,6,FThe money will go towards improving
OL,7,Fits network including by reducing
OL,8,Fspills and installing better
OL,9,Fmonitoring equipment. It will be paid
OL,10,Ffor by shareholders and not through
OL,11,Fcustomer bills.
OL,13,FAn Ofwat investigation found Wessex
OL,14,FWater failed to operate, maintain and
OL,15,Fupgrade its network to ensure it could
OL,16,Fcope with flows of sewage and
OL,17,Fwastewater.
